(38, 'Avicii', '1989-09-08', ' Stockholm', 'Avicii , his real name Tim Bergling , stylized in ΛVICII , born on September 8 , 1989in Stockholm 2 , is a Swedish producer and disc jockey . He has also produced titles under the pseudonyms of Tim Berg and Tom Hangs 3 .\r\n\r\nHe made himself known in Europe with his title Seek Bromance under his alias Tim Berg in 2011, which reached the Top 20 in several countries, and was a huge success worldwide with his single Levels . His piece Wake Me Up! is one of the hits of summer 2013 and dethrones many records 4 . According to US magazine Forbes , Avicii is one of thirty persons under 30 years of the most influential people in music 5 . He is listed since his debut in the benchmark ranking of the UK magazine DJ Magazine of the best world DJs in which he reaches the third place in 2012 and 2013.', 2);

